headline: These US Defense Stocks Could Be Relatively Insulated Against Tariffs, Morgan Stanley Says
summary: Defense companies that have kept U.S.-based supply chains for national security reasons could be relatively insulated from the impact of new tariffs, Morgan Stanley said Friday.
